OL,3,CPost Office lawyer 'covered up' flawed
OL,4,Cprosecution of pregnant sub-
OL,5,Cpostmistress
OL,7,FA former top Post Office lawyer knew
OL,8,Fof bugs which resulted in account
OL,9,Fdiscrepancies days before legal
OL,10,Fproceedings which saw a pregnant
OL,11,Fsubpostmistress jailed began and
OL,12,Fsubsequently lied to "cover up" that
OL,13,Ffact, an inquiry has heard.
OL,15,FSenior in-house lawyer Jarnail Singh
OL,16,Fwas copied into an email containing a
OL,17,Freport which identified the glitch but
OL,18,Fdenied knowledge of it for years -
OL,19,Fdespite saving the document and
OL,20,Fprinting it out, the Horizon IT
OL,21,FInquiry heard.
