OL,7,FMr Singh, who denied the claims, was a
OL,8,Fsenior lawyer at the Post Office and
OL,9,Fbecame head of criminal law in 2012
OL,10,Fafter it split with Royal Mail.
OL,12,FThe report, sent to Mr Singh just
OL,13,Fthree days before Seema Misra's case
OL,14,Fbegan in October 2010, described a bug
OL,15,F"that will result " and offered an
OL,16,Fexplanation for apparent cases of
OL,17,Ftheft among sub-postmasters, counsel
OL,18,Fto the inquiry Jason Beer KC said.
