OL,7,FMs Misra was eight weeks pregnant when
OL,8,Fshe was handed a 15-month prison
OL,9,Fsentence on her son's 10th birthday in
OL,10,FNovember 2010 after being accused of
OL,11,Fstealing #74,000 from her branch in
OL,12,FWest Byfleet, Surrey.
OL,14,FHer conviction was quashed by the
OL,15,FCourt of Appeal in 2021.
