OL,7,FMr Singh said he "wasn't made aware"
OL,8,Fof the report, written by Fujitsu
OL,9,Fengineer Gareth Jenkins and forwarded
OL,10,Fto lawyers Mr Singh and Juliet
OL,11,FMacfarlane by Rob Wilson, then head of
OL,12,Fcriminal law at the Post Office.
OL,14,FBut Mr Beer said a file address on the
OL,15,Fbottom of the document, which included
OL,16,FMr Singh's name, showed the lawyer had
OL,17,Fboth saved the report to his drive and
OL,18,Fprinted it out only nine minutes later.
